<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 09:13:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>葛兰素史克 (GSK) 以高达 14 亿美元完成对 Aiolos Bio 的收购</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/gsk-completes-acquisition-aiolos-bio-up-14-bln-2024-02-15/</link><description>葛兰素史克周四表示，已完成对 Aiolos Bio 的收购，Aiolos Bio 是一家专注于呼吸和炎症疾病的临床阶段生物制药公司。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 07:41:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/gsk-completes-acquisition-aiolos-bio-up-14-bln-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>独家：俄罗斯人利用中国合作伙伴在闲置的斯特兰蒂斯工厂生产雪铁龙汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/russians-use-chinese-partner-produce-citroen-cars-idled-stellantis-plant-2024-02-15/</link><description>汽车制造商 Stellantis 于 2022 年 4 月停止在俄罗斯的生产。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 06:33:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/russians-use-chinese-partner-produce-citroen-cars-idled-stellantis-plant-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>尽管销售预期下调，保乐力加股价仍上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/pernod-ricard-vise-un-ca-globalement-stable-pour-son-exercice-202324-2024-02-15/</link><description>保乐力加 (Pernod Ricard) 的股价周四上涨 6%，尽管这家法国烈酒制造商因美国和中国的改善未能实现而下调了全年销售预期和股票回购计划。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 06:24:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/pernod-ricard-vise-un-ca-globalement-stable-pour-son-exercice-202324-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>上次阿波罗登月任务半个世纪后，美国私人月球着陆器发射升空</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/private-us-moon-lander-launched-half-century-after-last-apollo-lunar-mission-2024-02-15/</link><description>周四早些时候，总部位于休斯敦的航空航天公司 Intuitive Machines 制造的月球着陆器从佛罗里达州发射升空，其任务是进行美国半个多世纪以来的首次月球着陆，也是私人航天器的首次着陆。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 06:10:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/private-us-moon-lander-launched-half-century-after-last-apollo-lunar-mission-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾承诺遵守南海行为准则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-committed-south-china-sea-code-conduct-2024-02-15/</link><description>菲律宾外长周四表示，菲律宾坚定致力于中国与东南亚国家之间就行为准则进行谈判，以避免南海对抗。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 05:47:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-committed-south-china-sea-code-conduct-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国抱怨前线岛屿附近发生致命事故后，台湾捍卫海岸警卫队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-defends-coast-guard-after-china-complains-over-fatal-accident-near-2024-02-15/</link><description>周四，台湾为其海岸警卫队的行动进行了辩护，此前一艘中国快艇因太靠近台湾前线岛屿而在试图逃离海岸警卫队船只时翻船，造成两人死亡。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 05:34:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-defends-coast-guard-after-china-complains-over-fatal-accident-near-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>随着经济放缓，一些中国年轻人放弃了企业工作，转而追求“自我时间”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/some-chinese-youth-spurn-corporate-jobs-me-time-economy-slows-2024-02-15/</link><description>面对经济放缓带来的就业前景黯淡，褚毅选择“平躺”，这是一个中文术语，用来描述那些工作只够花时间做自己喜欢的事情的人。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 01:09:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/some-chinese-youth-spurn-corporate-jobs-me-time-economy-slows-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>部分大众汽车因中国零件在美国港口延误</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/some-volkswagen-cars-delayed-us-ports-over-chinese-part-2024-02-14/</link><description>大众汽车周三表示，预计将在 3 月底之前解决因海关问题而滞留在美国港口的数千辆汽车的交付延误问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 20:54:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/some-volkswagen-cars-delayed-us-ports-over-chinese-part-2024-02-14/</guid></item><item><title>独家：德国对华投资创历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/german-investment-china-rises-new-record-high-2024-02-14/</link><description>IW研究所分析的德国央行官方数据显示，去年德国对华直接投资增长4.3%，达到创纪录的119亿欧元（127亿美元），占德国对外投资总额的比重也有所增加。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 09:16:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/german-investment-china-rises-new-record-high-2024-02-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国、美国主导的全球补充枯竭石油库存有望提振需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-us-led-global-refill-depleted-oil-stocks-seen-buoying-demand-2024-02-14/</link><description>分析师和交易商表示，随着中东紧张局势威胁到主要航道，推动补充耗尽的石油库存（尤其是在中国、美国和欧洲）可能会在未来几个月提振需求和价格。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 07:09:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-us-led-global-refill-depleted-oil-stocks-seen-buoying-demand-2024-02-14/</guid></item><item><title>台湾报告中国在附近进行另一次“战备巡逻”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-another-chinese-combat-readiness-patrol-nearby-2024-02-14/</link><description>台湾国防部表示，周三发现有 14 架中国空军飞机在台湾周围活动，并与中国军舰进行“联合战备巡逻”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 06:52:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-another-chinese-combat-readiness-patrol-nearby-2024-02-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国太平洋盟友所罗门群岛预计将于四月举行选举</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-pacific-ally-solomon-islands-expected-call-election-april-2024-02-14/</link><description>所罗门群岛预计将于下周举行四月份全国大选，随着各政党在这个太平洋岛国发起竞选活动，与中国的安全关系将成为一个关键问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 06:40:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-pacific-ally-solomon-islands-expected-call-election-april-2024-02-14/</guid></item><item><title>电梯制造商迅达预计 2024 年和中期利润率将实现稳健增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/schindler-expects-slight-revenue-growth-2024-2024-02-14/</link><description>作者：Ozan Ergenay 和 Louis van Boxel-Woolf</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 06:38:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/schindler-expects-slight-revenue-growth-2024-2024-02-14/</guid></item><item><title>日经新闻称，中国比亚迪计划在墨西哥新建电动汽车工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-plans-new-electric-vehicle-plant-mexico-says-nikkei-2024-02-13/</link><description>《日经新闻》周三援引该公司墨西哥负责人的话说，中国比亚迪有限公司将在墨西哥建立一家新的电动汽车（EV）工厂，该电动汽车制造商的目标是建立一个对美国的出口中心。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 18:06:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-plans-new-electric-vehicle-plant-mexico-says-nikkei-2024-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>独家：印度IT部担心在智能手机出口竞赛中输给中国和越南</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/india-it-ministry-fears-losing-out-china-vietnam-smartphone-exports-race-2024-02-13/</link><description>印度信息技术部副部长​​在路透社看到的政府文件中表示，印度在寻求成为主要智能手机出口中心时面临着输给中国和越南的风险，必须“迅速采取行动”以较低关税吸引全球公司。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 10:34:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/india-it-ministry-fears-losing-out-china-vietnam-smartphone-exports-race-2024-02-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>